00:24:00,063 --> 00:24:01,730
[Knock at door]

500
00:24:01,798 --> 00:24:03,632
Yeah?

501
00:24:03,700 --> 00:24:05,200
Jeannie?

502
00:24:05,268 --> 00:24:07,769
Jeannie, what are you
doing here? I--

503
00:24:07,837 --> 00:24:09,838
I'm--I mean,
is everything okay?

504
00:24:11,374 --> 00:24:13,008
- Are you okay?
- Yeah.

505
00:24:13,076 --> 00:24:15,578
I've never felt better,
actually,

506
00:24:15,645 --> 00:24:17,880
and without the pills.

507
00:24:17,948 --> 00:24:20,183
What you got there?
It smells good.

508
00:24:20,250 --> 00:24:21,584
I brought you
some herb-crusted chicken

509
00:24:21,652 --> 00:24:23,086
and scalloped potatoes.

510
00:24:23,153 --> 00:24:24,187
You hungry?

511
00:24:24,255 --> 00:24:27,390
Am I hungry?
You want to know...

512
00:24:27,458 --> 00:24:28,525
If I'm hungry.

513
00:24:28,593 --> 00:24:30,995
- Mm-hmm.
- Mm-hmm.

514
00:24:31,062 --> 00:24:31,962
What
[Laughs]

